{"tid":294893,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[日式料理] 47.6%纖維量！野菜牛肉鍋 -超級市場幻想","createTime":"2017-06-23T10:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T17:19:40.000Z","uid":106919,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93f849688eb2fe5b4fdf9cd10ef748740b425bc8","tid":294893,"uid":106919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/182555_2b37336f05652d578f659295f83d196e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F182555_2b37336f05652d578f659295f83d196e.jpg&h=7cec59b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>野菜牛肉鍋</strong><br />\n終於到星期五！好掛住日本既すき家... 多選擇得黎又抵，係窮拎至愛。上次教左日式高湯。今次用佢黎做分享一個多菜多益既牛肉鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以變做牛丼！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/183121_c84b89fee202c0c5dfdab2caa8d9f62d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F183121_c84b89fee202c0c5dfdab2caa8d9f62d.jpg&h=bad5a4b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/183122_bbabc1470314a9cac8d89a77d68c80e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F183122_bbabc1470314a9cac8d89a77d68c80e3.jpg&h=48a3be9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/183123_4a564997950b173a87a879605bec8fc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F183123_4a564997950b173a87a879605bec8fc8.jpg&h=09f9abb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳細食譜+分享請到blog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://wp.me/p8OUGU-1O\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp8OUGU-1O&d=aAFg1rLkOaTXOeQx7p2zg2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ef5b1cde\" target=\"_blank\">h